code: fit_RCMVN(   mu_hat,   sigma_hat,   mu0,   sigma0,   tau = min(diff(sort(mu_hat)))/2,   nu0 = NULL,   num_iters = 5000,   nu_reps = 2 )

title: Fit a Bayesian Rank-Clustered Estimation model for Network Meta-Analysis (RaCE-NMA). Recommended for internal use only; use mcmc_RCMVN instead. — fit_RCMVN
text: mu_hat vector estimated average relative intervention effects based previous NMA. jth entry effect intervention j. sigma_hat vector estimated standard deviations intervention. jth entry standard deviation intervention j. mu0 hyperparameter mu0, usually specified grand mean average intervention effects. sigma0 hyperparameter sigma_0, usually large number minimally informative. tau standard deviation Metropolis Hastings proposal distribution. nu0 numeric vector initialization intervention-specific mean parameters, mu, MCMC algorithm. Default NULL, indicating random initialization. num_iters numeric indicating total number outer MCMC iterations (.e., number times partition updated Gibbs sampler). nu_reps numeric indicating number times worth parameter drawn per update parameter partition. total num_itersxnu_reps samples posterior.

code: mcmc_RCMVN(   mu_hat,   sigma_hat,   mu0,   sigma0,   tau,   nu0 = NULL,   num_iters = 100,   nu_reps = 5,   chains = 4,   burn_prop = 0.5,   thin = 1,   seed = NULL,   suppressPrint = FALSE )

title: Fit a Bayesian Rank-Clustered Estimation model for Network Meta-Analysis (RaCE-NMA) using multiple MCMC chains — mcmc_RCMVN
text: mu_hat vector estimated average relative intervention effects based previous NMA. jth entry effect intervention j. sigma_hat vector estimated standard deviations intervention. jth entry standard deviation intervention j. mu0 hyperparameter mu0, usually specified grand mean average intervention effects. sigma0 hyperparameter sigma_0, usually large number minimally informative. tau standard deviation Metropolis Hastings proposal distribution. nu0 numeric vector initialization worth parameters, mu, MCMC algorithm. Default NULL, indicating random initialization. num_iters numeric indicating total number outer MCMC iterations (.e., number times partition updated Gibbs sampler). nu_reps numeric indicating number times worth parameter drawn per update parameter partition. total num_itersxnu_reps samples posterior. chains numeric indicating total number independent MCMC chains run. burn_prop numeric 0 1 indicating proportion MCMC samples chain removed burn-. thin numeric indicating every thin-th sample retained, save computational memory. seed numeric indicating random seed set running first MCMC chain. suppressPrint boolean indicating function print progress updates MCMC chains run.

title: Partition sampling in Bayesian RaCE-NMA models (internal use only) — sample_partition_normal
text: mu_hat vector estimated average relative intervention effects based previous NMA. jth entry effect intervention j. J numeric indicating total number interventions compared. nu vector indicating current values nu Gibbs sampler. g vector indicating current values g Gibbs sampler. K vector indicating current values K Gibbs sampler. mu0 hyperparameter mu0, usually specified grand mean average intervention effects. sigma0 hyperparameter sigma_0, usually large number minimally informative. sigma_hat vector estimated standard deviations intervention. jth entry standard deviation intervention j. tau standard deviation Metropolis Hastings proposal distribution. b_g probability "birth"ing new partition cluster, possible. Default 0.5. d_g probability "death"ing existing partition cluster, possible. Default 0.5.
